      "text": "⇒ [[Noise]] / order-from-noise production, not brought under control by standard repair procedures"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "c2909c4d457263cf",
      "text": "\"The noise can, of course, also establish itself as a permanent irritation that repeatedly pushes to the fore and permeates the coded information processing with penetrating noise that cannot be brought under control by the usual repair procedures. Severely disturbed areas within a system can then become ecological niches for the formation of parasitic social systems that are able to utilize the disturbing noise for themselves.\""
    },
